                            For the prototype in Major Project B, I mainly worked on the Workplace Health and Safety
                            feature, where I implemented a file-reading mechanism that read policies from a file and
                            created an object for each policy.
                            <br><br>
                            In collaboration with Thomas, we created the user.js file that represents the visiting user
                            of the website, of which stores all data as unique to that user. My part of this was to
                            implement get and set functions to the Workplace Health and Safety file and some additional
                            utility functions. As for app.js, I did the initial setup of the project and app.js, but
                            both Aslam, Thomas and I have worked in this file. Whereas Aslam mainly did the rendering
                            by using EJS, and Thomas worked on the /employee-folder and /monthly-report routes, I worked
                            on /whs-policies, /whs-policies:option and /player-reset.
                            <br><br>
                            The main focus we had for the prototype was to create one in-game month/ cycle. This was
                            important for us to achieve in order to have a testable product that used the API in a
                            dynamic manner.
                        </p>
